4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. The course has a duration of 16 weeks and includes classes in Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics.

Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and libraries like Pandas and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course covers both supervised and unsupervised learning models.

The classes are held three times a week, with a maximum class size of 12 students. Upon completion, students will receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations.

No previous experience is required for this course, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. Live classes are taught in the language of your campus.

To learn more about the course, visit the 4Geeks Academy website at [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). 

